00:11:29.089 --> 00:11:31.892 position:13% line:83% align:start
I've never seen you before
and I don't know who you are.

00:11:31.926 --> 00:11:33.394 position:30% line:83% align:start
But I can see
your point of strength

00:11:33.427 --> 00:11:34.695 position:5% line:89% align:start
