than a normal human being.

00:11:57.418 --> 00:11:59.887 position:21% line:83% align:start
In the end, you will
shed blood, just the same.

00:12:02.323 --> 00:12:03.490 position:16% line:89% align:start
I assume by your stance,

00:12:03.525 --> 00:12:05.059 position:19% line:83% align:start
