00:13:25.973 --> 00:13:30.110 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's only that old man.
He's your enemy. Destroy him!

00:13:30.144 --> 00:13:31.945 position:10% line:89% align:start
[F.F.] What... What is this?

00:13:31.979 --> 00:13:33.347 position:27% line:83% align:start
The reason that
old sack of shit

00:13:33.380 --> 00:13:35.916 position:24% line:83% align:start
can dodge bullets
is because of him?

00:13:35.949 --> 00:13:37.652 position:30% line:89% align:start
Here he comes.

00:13:37.686 --> 00:13:38.852 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[gasps]
-Hiyah!

00:13:41.656 --> 00:13:43.190 position:38% line:83% align:start
-[yells]
-[Kenzou] Hey-hey-hey!

00:13:43.924 --> 00:13:45.492 position:27% line:89% align:start
