00:13:45.527 --> 00:13:48.062 position:13% line:83% align:start
How does the walking dead
kick and punch so fast?

00:13:48.095 --> 00:13:50.497 position:24% line:83% align:start
To quote a phrase,
I can now enter the dragon.

00:13:51.265 --> 00:13:52.099 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hiyah!

00:13:54.569 --> 00:13:55.836 position:38% line:89% align:start
