of F.F.'s head.

00:14:11.653 --> 00:14:12.853 position:33% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] Ugh!
[grunts]

00:14:16.023 --> 00:14:18.058 position:19% line:89% align:start
Shit! That was close.

00:14:18.092 --> 00:14:20.994 position:10% line:83% align:start
But still, F.F. blocked it.
That was so badass!

00:14:21.028 --> 00:14:24.031 position:10% line:83% align:start
I noticed as soon as Kenzou
touched that dragon Stand,

00:14:24.064 --> 00:14:26.534 position:21% line:83% align:start
