at that same moment.

00:14:26.568 --> 00:14:29.236 position:19% line:83% align:start
A smoked screen so we
won't see his attack coming.

00:14:34.942 --> 00:14:38.112 position:10% line:83% align:start
[F.F.] Oh, shit! What's that
dragon behind him now?

00:14:38.145 --> 00:14:40.981 position:24% line:83% align:start
When you touch it,
does your other arm tear off?

00:14:41.014 --> 00:14:42.983 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's just like the User,
the attack was weak.

00:14:43.384 --> 00:14:44.918 position:35% line:89% align:start
No, F.F.!

00:14:44.952 --> 00:14:47.888 position:21% line:83% align:start
This battle's result
is already decided.

00:14:47.921 --> 00:14:49.758 position:10% line:89% align:start
But it's not like anyone can

00:14:49.791 --> 00:14:51.325 position:27% line:83% align:start
actually predict
what happens, though.

00:14:51.358 --> 00:14:54.829 position:13% line:83% align:start
Hiyah! And you, pipe down!
You talked too much.

00:14:54.863 --> 00:14:56.029 position:30% line:83% align:start
Why would you
give away everything?

00:14:56.063 --> 00:14:58.098 position:7% line:83% align:start
You're supposed to be neutral!
Remember that?

00:14:58.132 --> 00:15:00.668 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Drake's Dream] You're
operating in bad faith, though.

00:15:00.702 --> 00:15:02.771 position:30% line:83% align:start
You must share
your secret with her.

00:15:02.804 --> 00:15:04.138 position:10% line:89% align:start
[suspenseful music playing]

00:15:05.339 --> 00:15:06.440 position:33% line:89% align:start
[squeaking]

00:15:16.450 --> 00:15:17.552 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:21.455 --> 00:15:22.289 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:23.792 --> 00:15:24.559 position:38% line:89% align:start
[grunts]

00:15:28.095 --> 00:15:30.632 position:35% line:83% align:start
Oh, dear!
You opened your mouth.

00:15:31.733 --> 00:15:32.667 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Hiyah!
-[F.F. grunts]

00:15:36.470 --> 00:15:39.072 position:27% line:89% align:start
F.F.! Look out!

00:15:39.106 --> 00:15:41.576 position:7% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] There is no freaking
way that was a coincidence.

00:15:41.609 --> 00:15:43.678 position:19% line:83% align:start
That inmate's glasses
flew straight at F.F.

00:15:43.711 --> 00:15:46.180 position:19% line:83% align:start
and lodged themselves
in her face?

00:15:46.213 --> 00:15:48.182 position:19% line:83% align:start
Unfortunate direction.
[sighs]

00:15:48.883 --> 00:15:50.652 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'm starting to understand.

00:15:50.685 --> 00:15:52.219 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's feng shui in action.

00:15:52.252 --> 00:15:53.053 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:15:53.086 --> 00:15:55.590 position:30% line:83% align:start
It's geomancy
for the East Asians.

00:15:55.623 --> 00:15:57.224 position:16% line:89% align:start
Watch Kenzou's movements

00:15:57.257 --> 00:15:59.393 position:21% line:83% align:start
as if he's adjusting
to a certain direction.

00:15:59.426 --> 00:16:03.263 position:5% line:83% align:start
Attacks coming from there, one
direction as if pre-determined,

00:16:03.297 --> 00:16:06.200 position:10% line:83% align:start
and that Stand on his hand,
it just works.

00:16:06.233 --> 00:16:09.637 position:5% line:83% align:start
The only conclusion to be drawn
is, with that dragon Stand,

00:16:09.671 --> 00:16:12.473 position:10% line:83% align:start
Kenzou can perfectly control
the direction of his attacks.

00:16:13.474 --> 00:16:15.777 position:16% line:89% align:start
Feng shui? What is that?

00:16:15.810 --> 00:16:17.478 position:21% line:83% align:start
And what do you mean
by direction?

00:16:18.378 --> 00:16:19.714 position:30% line:89% align:start
I'll explain.

00:16:19.747 --> 00:16:23.350 position:5% line:83% align:start
It's as famous as astrology and
tarot card reading, maybe more,

00:16:24.084 --> 00:16:25.887 position:7% line:89% align:start
but it's not fortune telling.

00:16:25.920 --> 00:16:28.623 position:19% line:83% align:start
East Asian philosophy
highlights the idea

00:16:28.656 --> 00:16:31.191 position:10% line:83% align:start
that there are natural paths
of energy in the natural world

00:16:31.225 --> 00:16:33.093 position:27% line:83% align:start
such as the flow
of wind and water.

00:16:33.126 --> 00:16:35.797 position:16% line:83% align:start
By knowing the direction
in which nature is flowing,

00:16:35.830 --> 00:16:39.233 position:19% line:83% align:start
it helps people choose
similar paths for their lives.

00:16:39.266 --> 00:16:40.735 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Anastasia] Here's an example.

00:16:40.768 --> 00:16:42.236 position:7% line:89% align:start
Feng shui is used to determine

00:16:42.269 --> 00:16:45.205 position:19% line:83% align:start
the good and bad areas
of the land, house, and room.

00:16:45.239 --> 00:16:47.842 position:21% line:83% align:start
If the direction of
the land or house is bad,

00:16:47.876 --> 00:16:49.544 position:30% line:83% align:start
it will affect
the resident's health,

00:16:49.577 --> 00:16:53.113 position:5% line:83% align:start
fortune and even the whole
family's well-being negatively.

00:16:53.848 --> 00:16:55.650 position:10% line:89% align:start
In times of war, it is said

00:16:55.683 --> 00:16:57.785 position:24% line:83% align:start
that they checked
the feng shui of the castle

00:16:57.819 --> 00:16:59.386 position:13% line:89% align:start
and thus, could determine

00:16:59.419 --> 00:17:01.121 position:13% line:83% align:start
the most advantageous area
of the fortress

00:17:01.154 --> 00:17:03.725 position:19% line:83% align:start
they could attack from
to bring down the enemy.

00:17:03.758 --> 00:17:05.225 position:24% line:89% align:start
On the other hand,

00:17:05.259 --> 00:17:07.729 position:19% line:83% align:start
if you build a shrine
in the weak zone of the castle,

00:17:07.762 --> 00:17:10.130 position:10% line:89% align:start
it can calm the evil energy.

00:17:10.163 --> 00:17:13.066 position:19% line:83% align:start
The castle will gain a
furthermore solidified defense.

00:17:14.702 --> 00:17:17.539 position:5% line:83% align:start
And of course, this same theory
of feng shui

00:17:17.572 --> 00:17:19.707 position:21% line:83% align:start
can also be applied
to human bodies.

00:17:19.741 --> 00:17:22.442 position:19% line:83% align:start
There's even an attack
called feng shui assassination.

00:17:23.011 --> 00:17:23.978 position:38% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:17:24.012 --> 00:17:25.412 position:24% line:83% align:start
If you can control
the direction

00:17:25.445 --> 00:17:27.180 position:21% line:83% align:start
from which to attack
your enemy,

00:17:27.214 --> 00:17:30.518 position:16% line:83% align:start
you're almost guaranteed
a victory over them.

00:17:30.552 --> 00:17:33.253 position:21% line:83% align:start
No matter how alert
and prepared the target is,

00:17:33.287 --> 00:17:35.890 position:5% line:83% align:start
you'll be able to approach them
without being noticed,

00:17:35.924 --> 00:17:37.926 position:33% line:83% align:start
leaving them
completely vulnerable,

00:17:37.959 --> 00:17:39.827 position:24% line:83% align:start
and you can easily
assassinate them.

00:17:39.861 --> 00:17:41.194 position:30% line:89% align:start
That means...

00:17:42.162 --> 00:17:44.231 position:19% line:89% align:start
...unlucky direction.

00:17:44.264 --> 00:17:45.767 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] I think
we've now established

00:17:45.800 --> 00:17:47.735 position:7% line:89% align:start
the secret of Kenzou's Stand.

00:17:47.769 --> 00:17:51.204 position:24% line:83% align:start
The unlucky course
pointing straight toward F.F.

00:17:51.238 --> 00:17:54.008 position:7% line:83% align:start
That dragon Stand is pointing
out the precise direction

00:17:54.042 --> 00:17:55.843 position:16% line:83% align:start
for Kenzou to kill them
fast and easy.

00:17:56.744 --> 00:17:58.378 position:10% line:89% align:start
And at some point very soon,

00:17:58.412 --> 00:18:00.748 position:19% line:83% align:start
his attack will merge
with that floating dragon.

00:18:00.782 --> 00:18:04.052 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid F.F.'s fate
has already been decided.

00:18:04.084 --> 00:18:05.987 position:16% line:89% align:start
I can't believe Kenzou.

00:18:06.020 --> 00:18:07.989 position:10% line:83% align:start
He's spent the last 40 years
in prison

00:18:08.022 --> 00:18:10.157 position:16% line:83% align:start
mastering the feng shui
assassination,

00:18:10.190 --> 00:18:13.628 position:16% line:83% align:start
and that skill developed
as his Stand power.

00:18:13.661 --> 00:18:16.598 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] Feng shui!
The direction to proceed!

00:18:16.631 --> 00:18:17.699 position:21% line:83% align:start
