-[F.F. breathes]

00:18:17.732 --> 00:18:19.667 position:13% line:89% align:start
...when he was on defense!

00:18:19.701 --> 00:18:21.002 position:19% line:89% align:start
That would explain it.

00:18:21.035 --> 00:18:22.570 position:24% line:83% align:start
That's why not one
of the bullets

00:18:22.604 --> 00:18:23.470 position:16% line:89% align:start
