00:18:23.938 --> 00:18:25.172 position:30% line:89% align:start
Unbelievable!

00:18:25.205 --> 00:18:28.375 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're saying the feng shui
also protected him

00:18:28.408 --> 00:18:30.745 position:19% line:83% align:start
as well as helped him
try to kill them?

00:18:30.778 --> 00:18:32.212 position:35% line:89% align:start
Yes, I am.

00:18:32.245 --> 00:18:35.215 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Anastasia] When he holds
that dragon Stand in his hands,

00:18:35.248 --> 00:18:37.885 position:16% line:83% align:start
