launches his attack.

00:18:44.424 --> 00:18:47.595 position:10% line:83% align:start
The dragon is trying to show
the direct line to kill again.

00:18:47.629 --> 00:18:48.630 position:33% line:89% align:start
F.F.! Wait!

00:18:48.663 --> 00:18:50.263 position:24% line:83% align:start
Those glasses were
deliberately made

00:18:50.297 --> 00:18:52.000 position:7% line:89% align:start
