00:18:52.033 --> 00:18:53.233 position:19% line:89% align:start
Hold the old man off.

00:18:53.266 --> 00:18:55.803 position:10% line:83% align:start
Don't let him get too close
to that dragon.

00:18:55.837 --> 00:18:58.338 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Jolyne] I know! It makes
no fucking sense to me, either.

00:18:58.372 --> 00:19:00.340 position:30% line:83% align:start
But seriously,
whatever you do,

00:19:00.374 --> 00:19:02.175 position:21% line:83% align:start
