to touch it.

00:19:02.209 --> 00:19:05.880 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let's go! Nicely done,
Drake's Dream. Thank you!

00:19:05.913 --> 00:19:07.247 position:10% line:89% align:start
They figured it out because

00:19:07.280 --> 00:19:09.316 position:30% line:83% align:start
